		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蛇姬扔出钩锁进行一段位移，立即接开炮发射8枚籽弹，每枚籽弹造成<span color="#99ff85">30%,15%,7.5%,3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，蛇姬将装弹炮筒，发射1枚迫击草球，造成<span color="#99ff85">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蛇姬驱使灵力，迂旋炮筒造成<span color="#99ff85">80%</span><span>伤害，接着捶地，促使炮筒喷出9枚草球，每枚草球造成</span><span color="#99ff85">100%,50%</span><span>伤害。技能施放后在空中凝聚3枚</span><span textDecoration="underline">钩爪</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蛇姬借助钩爪进行空战，会连续发射最多6枚草球进行攻击，每枚草球造成<span color="#99ff85">66%</span><span>伤害。攻击后会移到其他钩爪处。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="975" width="425" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">钩爪：<span color="#99ff85">5草</span><span>盾，一共3枚，击破蛇姬所在钩爪可使其坠落瘫痪；一段时间后也会自行消失。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
