		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="437" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蛇姬拿着炮筒进行划、砸2段攻击，分别造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%,70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
